videos.description: Louisville guard Lamarr Kimble gets his defender in the air with a pump fake and spins around to knock down the midrange jump shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Louisville's Kimble fools defender and hits jumper) 2020/02/24

videos.headline: Louisville's Kimble fools defender and hits jumper

videos.description: Trent Forrest fires a deep pass into the paint for Dominik Olejniczak who takes it to the hoop for a layup while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Forrest's long pass sets up Olejniczak's and-1) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: Forrest's long pass sets up Olejniczak's and-1

videos.description: Ryan McMahon pulls up for a 3-pointer from the Seminoles' logo in the first half of action.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Louisville's McMahon drains 3 from the logo) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: Louisville's McMahon drains 3 from the logo

videos.description: Louisville's David Johnson works his way into the paint and trips up his defender for a nice bucket plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson doesn't let FSU defense get in his way) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: Johnson doesn't let FSU defense get in his way

videos.description: Florida State's RaiQuan Gray pushes his way to the hoop under pressure and gets an and-1 to fall in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gray fights his way to the hoop for and-1) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: Gray fights his way to the hoop for and-1

videos.description: M.J. Walker runs into the official in transition and immediately hits the hardwood in pain before heading back to the locker room in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's Walker collides with ref, leaves with apparent ankle injury) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: FSU's Walker collides with ref, leaves with apparent ankle injury

videos.description: Ryan McMahon appears to get into a verbal altercation and doesn't immediately retreat to his team's side during the timeout, forcing an official to escort him back.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ref escorts Louisville's McMahon away from FSU's huddle) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: Ref escorts Louisville's McMahon away from FSU's huddle

videos.description: Patrick Williams adds to Florida State's dominating second half vs. Louisville with a monster slam off a Cardinals turnover.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams' one-handed slam gets FSU fans on their feet) 2020/2/24

videos.headline: Williams' one-handed slam gets FSU fans on their feet
